OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining warm with light winds.
OL,7,FProbably cloudy at times Monday and
OL,8,FTuesday, with potential for a few
OL,9,Fshowers on Monday, otherwise dry.
OL,10,FWednesday sunnier conditions are
OL,11,Flikely.
